  "title": "",
  "body": " Iryna makes $22 an hour and got a raise of $3 per hour. Sundar currently makes $19 an hour and got a raise of $2.85. Who got a larger raise relatively?  Using the formula percent = , we can compare the two raises.    Iryna:   .  Iryna's raise was about 13.6% of her wage.    Sundar:   .  Sundar's raise was 15% of his wage.    Iryna had a bigger raise in terms of dollar amount, but in terms of percentage, Sundar's raise was bigger.  "
